<h1 id="step-6">Step 6</h1>
<p><strong>Describe how you might change the simulation to learn more about the operating characteristics of your chosen method for constructing the 95% confidence interval.</strong></p>

<p>I think I will choose to use bigger distribution to test the process, likes set the <em>N</em> as 5000 or 10000. And I could calculate the other quantile of the distributions to find out is there any different. After that, maybe I will use other distribution but not standard normal distribution, such as gamma or beta distribution.</p>
